descriptionHtml:
Hi there!

I decided to upload one of my characters presets, Maya(nord) to the nexus.

I also uploaded a bonus one for breton.

I might make them into followers at some point, but because my skill with creating followers through mod manager is less than zero, this may take some time


Requirements(And credits)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion by HHaleyy[/url] (Needs the skin textures, brows and freckles from this. Also uses the updated make up tintmasks)
SG hair 268 edition by Hellosanta (I can't put any link to this, use google)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?]Dimonized UNP Female Body by Dimon99[/url] (You can also use CBBE, but I used UNP.)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56056/?]Mikan Eyes by Nerune2525[/url] (Needs the eyes from this)

Armor used for Maya
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60814/?]Katarina Armor by Newermind43[/url]

Armor used for Ilina
Fine Imperial dress (Find it on google)

I also used [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13049/?]Imaginator by MGE[/url] with these settings:
Parchment overlay 0.2
Pop photoshoot 0.1
Saturation -10
Sun -2
Sky 3
Blue 8
Orange 2

And added one screenshot for both characters where I have [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52718/?]ICBINE 2 by ElSopa[/url] turned on.

Please do not post screenshots of them with nudity, I would prefer to keep this mod page SFW.
author: Thylahyde
